
                       geant4-01-00-ref-02
                       ===================

geant4-01-00-ref-02 is geant4-01-00-ref-01 plus:

greps-V01-00-00       - Added G4Polyhedron::Transform and InvertFacets.
source-gmk-V01-00-00  - Added null operator (:) to each line so that
                        exit status is always OK.
global-V01-00-00      - Syncronized changes with HEAD (mainly CVS headers).
                      - Fixed truncation problem in G4Poisson.hh.
                      - Removed tphdict_test.cc and tvhdict_test.cc in
                        STLInterface/test.
                      - Added wrapper for HP-aCC for missing <fstream>
                        standard header.
                      - Removed G4USE_STL from globals.hh and
                        G4Timer[.hh.cc].
config-V01-00-00      - Syncronized with HEAD.
                      - Cosmetic improvement to echo line in binmake.gmk.
examples-V01-00-00    - N02, N03: Introduced ExN0nSteppingVerbose.
                      - N04: Introduced 10 TeV mu- in
                        exampleN04.EMtest.in.
                      - All reference files updated.
